contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|keto}} {{For|the town in Ecuador frequently misspelled as ''Keto'' or ''Keeto''|Quito}} '''Keto''' can refer to: * The [[Keto people]], an ethnic group of the Siberian North. * [[Ceto]] or Keto, a sea goddess in Greek mythology. * [[Ketone]] or keto group, the functional group in the chemical compounds ketones. * [[Ketoconazole]], a medication that can inhibit the production of testosterone in both the testes and adrenal gland. * [[Ketogenic diet]] * [[Low-carbohydrate diet]] * ''Ketō'' (毛唐) or ''ketōjin'' (毛唐人), a derogatory term in Japanese referring to a white person (see also ''[[gaijin]]'') {{disambig}}
